# CODEOWNERS (template) — replace the placeholder teams below with real
# GitHub usernames/teams once the team is formed. GitHub ignores entries
# whose owners don't resolve, so this file is inert until then.
#
# Format: <path pattern>  <owner(s)>

# Default owners for everything
*                                @your-org/maintainers

# Security-sensitive areas require security review
/security/                      @your-org/security
/.claude/agents/security-*.md   @your-org/security
/.claude/skills/*-review/        @your-org/security

# CI/CD and deployment pipeline
/.github/workflows/             @your-org/devops
/ci/                              @your-org/devops

# Architecture decisions and shared code
/docs/adr/                       @your-org/architecture
/shared/                          @your-org/architecture
